				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ IPMEM=\frac{\sum \limits_{i=1}^7{\rho}_i{x}_i}{432} $$\end{document}IPMEM=∑i=17ρixi432

The quantitative values (Mi) and the relevance factor (ρi) of each variable were substituted in the expression (3),\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ {\displaystyle \begin{array}{l}{IPMEM}_{V1}=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^7{\rho}_i{x}_i}{432}=\frac{\rho_1\left({x}_1\right)+{\rho}_2\left({x}_2\right)+{\rho}_3\left({x}_3\right)+{\rho}_4\left({x}_4\right)+{\rho}_5\left({x}_5\right)+{\rho}_6\left({x}_6\right)+{\rho}_7\left({x}_7\right)}{432}\\ {}{IPMEM}_{V1}=\frac{10(15)+8(8)+7(5)+7(1)+6(10)+5(5)+4(10)}{432}=0.88\end{array}} $$\end{document}IPMEMV1=∑i=17ρixi432=ρ1x1+ρ2x2+ρ3x3+ρ4x4+ρ5x5+ρ6x6+ρ7x7432IPMEMV1=1015+88+75+71+610+55+410432=0.88
